{
  "chapter": 68,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十八回\"暗藏奸诈\"讲述两条线索交织推进。燕南天与花无缺并肩离开花林，讨论铁心兰去向与铜先生来历，燕南天怀疑铜先生是他人化名改扮。与此同时，铜先生将江小鱼带回客栈，江小鱼虽身不能动，却以机智百出的手段戏弄铜先生——借上茅房之名争取行动自由，又以绝食相威胁逼迫铜先生带他去吃饭。燕南天、花无缺与江别鹤在扬子江酒楼相遇，江别鹤见到燕南天后惊恐万状，却强装镇定陪饮。燕南天醉后谈及江琴出卖江二弟的往事，江别鹤心惊胆战。小鱼儿与铜先生亦来到扬子江酒楼大吃大喝，小鱼儿不断以言语挑衅铜先生，铜先生怒而拍碎桌椅却无可奈何。夜深后三人醉归客栈，江别鹤暗中吐酒频频劝饮，终将燕南天与花无缺灌醉，暗藏奸诈之心昭然若揭。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "铁心兰是往哪里走的？你也未曾瞧见么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江小鱼此刻也不知是在哪里？……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他是何时落入那'铜先生'掌中的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "昨天晚上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "江湖中又怎会有个'铜先生'？他既有那么高的武功，我怎会未曾闻及？……你可知道他的来历？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "在下只知他武功之高，不可思议，却也不知他的来历。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是我猜得不错，他必定是别人化名改扮的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "但普天之下谁会有那么高的武功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "移花宫主……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "家师为何要改扮成别人？家师又为何要瞒住我？这对他老人家又有何好处？燕大侠你可想得出任何原因来么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想不出……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你想，那'铜先生'会将江小鱼带到何处去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "在下也想不出。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我睡了很久了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "很……很久了。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你一直坐在这里守着我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我占了你的床，让你不能睡觉，真抱歉得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你……你的腿没有伤？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我有个毛病，一睡醒就要……就要上茅房。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不许去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "不许去，我就要拉在裤子上了，那可臭得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你……你敢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "一个人无论有多凶，多厉害，他就算能杀人、放火，但可也没法子叫别人不屙屎的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你要我不拉屎，只有一个法子，那就是立刻杀了我，否则……否则我现在就已忍不住了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不行……这里不行……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你让我出去了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你滚出去吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你若不放心，就在茅房外看着我吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你死在里面了么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好几天的存货，一次出清，自然要费些功夫。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "现在咱们该去吃饭了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你……你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "吃饭屙屎，本是最普通的事，这又有什么好奇怪的？……你难道从未听见过一个人要吃饭么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我虽不能禁止你……你上茅房，但却能禁止你吃饭的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你不许我吃饭？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我给你吃的时候，你才能吃，否则你就闭起嘴！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但嘴却是长在我脸上的，是么？所以，我要吃饭的时候，你就得给我吃，否则我就永远也不吃了。我若活活饿死了，你的计划也完了……你明白了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "你……你敢对我如此说话？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我虽打不过你，但要饿死自己，你可也没法子，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你喝酒么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "还可喝两杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，咱们就去喝两杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "江浙菜甜，北方菜淡，还是四川菜，又咸又辣又麻，那才合男子汉大丈夫的口味．你意下如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "这城里有家扬子江酒楼，据说倒是名厨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ge_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "那大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "花公子来了。就在下面，好像也要上楼来喝酒。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yi_ge_da_han",
      "text": "他一个人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ge_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "那大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "他还带着个穿得又破又烂的瘦长汉子，好像是……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快……快想法子去挡他们一挡。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "不想江兄也在这里。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "是……是……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "这位就是近来江湖盛传的'江南大侠'江别鹤么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不……不敢。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "好，咱们就坐在一起，喝两杯吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江兄为何不坐下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "燕某足迹虽未踏入江湖，却也久闻江兄侠名，今日少不得要痛痛快快和你喝上两杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈先敬燕大侠一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江兄这杯酒，为何还不喝下去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚辈也早已久仰燕大侠侠名，不想今日得见，当真荣幸之至。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "不错，你我初次相见，倒真该痛饮一场才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "正是该痛饮一场，不醉不归。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个不醉不归……来，快拿三十斤酒来！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你别着急，饭铺就算打烊，只要你肯花银子，连鬼都会推磨，何愁饭铺不为你开门。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这里就有家饭铺，你叫门吧。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这家饭铺叫三和楼，是江浙菜，不行……嗯，这里还有家真北平，一定是北方菜，也不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "为何不行？你难道不能将就些？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "不行，一个人可以对不起朋友，但却万万不能对不起自己的肠胃。因为朋友到你倒霉时，都会跑的，但肠胃却跟你一辈子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "世上人人都怕我，你……你为何不怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我明知你绝不会自己动手杀我的，我为何要怕你？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "其实你也不必生气，你明知你越生气，我就越开心，又何必定要和自己过不去呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们发什么呆，这位大爷脸上戴的虽然是青铜，腰里却多的是金子，财神爷上门，你们还不赶紧招呼。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "那店伙",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "抱……抱歉得很，小店已经打烊了。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管你们打烊没有，他要吃什么，你们就送什么上来，只要少了一样，你们这四个人休想有一个活着。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "痛快痛快，和你这样的人出来吃饭，当真再痛快不过。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "深更半夜的，也不必弄太多菜了，马马虎虎就这几样吧，但酒却要上好的，竹叶青还是花雕都行，先来个二三十斤。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "那店伙",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "抱歉……小……小店的酒，已经被方才三位客官喝光了。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喝光了就到别处去买，三十斤，少了一斤，要你的脑袋！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你为何不坐下来，你这样站着，我怎么吃得下？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这酒菜倒都不错，你为何不来吃一些，你若气得吃不下，饿坏了身子，我心里也不舒服的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "嘴是长在你身上的，你不吃，我也没法子，但你这样，既不吃，又不睡，怎么受得了呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "桌子又没有得罪你，你何苦跟它过不去……依我看，你不如还是放了我吧，也免得自己受这活罪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "放了你？休想！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "老实告诉你，其实你现在就算放了我，我也不走的，睡觉有人保镖，喝酒有人付账。这么开心的日子，到哪里找去。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我正是要你现在活得开心些．这样你死时才会更痛苦。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我问你，我和你素不相识，你为何如此恨我？你既如此恨我，又为什么不肯自己动手杀了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这其中秘密，你永远也不会知道的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人若是永远无法知道自己最切身的秘密，这岂非是世上最残忍、最悲惨的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_jiang_xiao_yu",
      "text": "不错，这正是世上最残忍、最悲惨的事，我敢负责担保，这悲惨的命运，你逃也逃不了的，只因世上绝对没有人能揭穿这秘密。所以你现在只管开心吧，只要你真能开心，你不妨尽量多开心些。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此……此话怎讲？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我那江二弟，温厚善良，可算世上第一个大好人，但还有江琴……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我那江二弟虽将江琴视如兄弟手足一般，但这狼心狗肺的奴才，竟在暗中串通别人，将他出卖了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "那江……江琴竟如此可恶？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这奴才竟不知躲到哪里去了，我竟找不着他……我若找着他，不将他骨头一根根捏碎才怪。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "晚……晚辈并非江……江琴，燕大侠莫要将晚辈的手也捏碎。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三更半夜，这几人必定不干好事，我瞧瞧去。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "有我在此，还用得着你去瞧么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冀人燕南天在此，上线开扒的朋友，全出来吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住，一个也不许跑！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有燕某在这城里，你们居然还想为非作歹，难道不要命了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_xing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夜行人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "小人们不知燕大侠又重出江湖，望燕大侠恕罪。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但江大侠在这城里，你们难道也不知道？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "念在你们坏事还未做出，每个人打自己二十个耳刮子。快滚吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人能有这样的声名，才算不虚此生了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "普天之下，有这样声名的人，只怕也不只燕大侠一个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，你还不服我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "他们若知道移花宫有人在此，只怕跑得更快的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "要你这样的人佩服，当真不是容易事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "贤弟，燕大侠似已有些醉了，你我不如和燕南天别过，赶紧走吧！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我只怕要和江兄别过了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "贤弟你……你难道要和燕大侠同行么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "令师若是知道，只怕有些不便吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "家师纵然知道，我也是要和他一起走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你……你们要去哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "去找江小鱼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "这客栈燕大侠可要再进去喝两杯么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你果然善体人意……走，咱们进去！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒逢知己，不醉不归，来，再喝一杯……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 68,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    }
  ],
  "new_entities": {
    "characters": [
      {
        "id": "char_jiang_bie_he",
        "name": "江别鹤",
        "alias": [
          "江大侠"
        ],
        "identity": "江南大侠",
        "faction": "无",
        "role": "villain",
        "archetype": "scholar",
        "rank": "登堂入室",
